<br>
today i nuked a crapy mob thingy, crit 3880(or so) mob was at 50 when nuke landed, ranger, sk 2 pets beating on it, no agro, i could sit and whatever.<br>
<br>
few minutes later i nuke mob with the same name. resisted, it was at 45% when nuked, same SK, ranger, 2 pets beating on it, i had agro for the rest of the fight. /boggle <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=silverbladetheenchanter>Silverblade the Enchanter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magi Draconis</span><br>  Posts: 2150<br> <font color=#333333>(10/30/02 9:49:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7647.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excaliburthumb1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: agro!</span><hr size=1> Firebolt of Talon is ENORMOUS aggro, and should be used carefully <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
